quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,"The craving for more [worldly wealth and power] keeps you engrossed"
  102,2,Until you embrace the graves
  102,3,Nay! You shall soon come to know
  102,4,Nay again! You shall soon come to know
  102,5,"Nay, if you but knew with certain knowledge"
  102,6,You shall surely see the Hell
  102,7,Then you shall surely see it with eye of certitude
  102,8,"And then, on that Day, you shall surely be questioned about the bounties you enjoyed"